Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.00,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(544,317)}取名叫「名古屋」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.00,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(85,370)}羽 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.00,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(56,482)}鸡饲料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷雫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好参加此次会议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么鸡棚要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我已经查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的答案都在网络上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家附近有个建材超市哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去那里买材料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家一起去吧 这周双休一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,32)}祝养鸡委员会成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(216,85)}第一回会议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(106,125)}取名叫「名古屋」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(403,165)}羽 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,202)}鸡饲料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:57.91,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,258)}鸡棚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.99,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动之后再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和同学一起度过的双休
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.62,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定了的话 就是那个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:01.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:05.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是碰面啊 时间地点啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:10.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 反正是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候是不是应该答应下来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:22.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 虽然说了喜欢 那也只是气氛推动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:35.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我这份心意没有让春感到快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:44.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为社团活动结束的早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去里面等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:57.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我不擅长和男生单独相处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不要再来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:12.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗 那人好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 棒球少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐原同学你认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我经常来这里玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:25.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说少年 你和春也是朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是朋友不如说是同学啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去打一局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:34.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:38.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能轻易把钱借给别人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:45.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 球棒要这么握着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:52.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉 我弟把闹钟弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:54.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 不是很帅气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预算不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去借啊 按揭贷款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:07.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 鸡又不交税
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:10.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 别管他们了 我们去找材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:16.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色 金色 金色 茶色 黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 正好有些话要和你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷同学 L尺寸是指什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿佐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮冬瓜你干吗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷同学 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳 还以为会打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 我连架都没打过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们先到外面去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:56.63,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面 后面 水谷同学有危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了 我们快跑吧 春！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑的真慢呢 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 对不起 夏目同学能帮忙买回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙可能还在那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我过去帮忙提东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 你就陪着水谷同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:08:59.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:08.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过每次都被你吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用一只手就把人扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和自己刚刚拒绝过的人说点什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:33.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是平常 一定会拒绝照顾鸡这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日要你出来 你也绝对会拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:37.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说确实没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人在奇怪的地方真是敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:53.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没骗我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个家伙真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…是在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都买好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把木头锯成一段一段好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说要店员帮我们锯好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这种漂亮的鸡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我们自己做根本不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:38.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说 我们选的还是最简单易懂的网站了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说买那个小屋就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:44.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎么了 怎么了 已经累垮了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锯子吗？好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你们要电锯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电锯的话早说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！我去拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:59.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去买一点冰 你们想吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要GARIGARI苏打冰棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要巨无霸巧克力冰淇淋夹心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能完成吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你喽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:17.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用这么慌张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是真的有话要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也觉得有点对不起春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:32.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但问题是从那之后就联系不上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那现在道歉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说对不对 水谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们之前伤害了人家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才想起道歉实在很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 想道歉的话就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:49.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要别打扰到我们做事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人好冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也学会察言观色啊 我们是想让你当和事佬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！你们这群家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:10.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下嘛 春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.43,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是来找她说些话的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是不是呢？水谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁准你碰雫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊！臭小子 你听人家说话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你就讨厌 山贤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.52,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能别动不动就动手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.61,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙到底是干什么来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:28.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说想来和你和好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:39.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了表明心意他们好像要帮忙盖鸡屋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么要干这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:47.50,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和好的话 这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.54,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 早点说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊 一起来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:57.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种场景经常在电视上看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.54,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是好朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:06.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙真的好吗 你喜欢这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买冰回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕了点路所以冰有点化了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 变多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！超级可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.34,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个组合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.61,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好好扶好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小水 这些人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:25.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使唤别人就可以不费力的完成 太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然经过这些事 鸡屋总算顺利完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:32.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们干了件好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把名古屋带来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢 祝贺你哦 水谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是什么都没做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了不许碰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊！混蛋！你够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有点烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周就可以把鸡屋带到学校去 好期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:14.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得带那种东西去会被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们把鸡小屋放到草丛里就没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:25.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点可怕 不过春同学那些朋友真是不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么看我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我往这边走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这边 可以一起走一段路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那星期一见哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:42.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:42.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 为什么叫名古屋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在吐槽太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡的名字的话名古屋不好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 送到这里就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你客气什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和雫多待一会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有勇气抬头看他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说人的一生的幸福和不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是上帝决定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过终点大家都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是「正负相消」的道理？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不过是一种诡辩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 最近总是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说遇到雫是我的幸运的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么之前都是些乱七八糟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自从与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到的都是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我投降！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢春！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么努力想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想象不出别人的心情是如何的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:10.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 就只能由我直接说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:15.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候春说了 太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢我 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我让你困扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:30.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我已经喜欢上春了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…还真是坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为你在那装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:45.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…并没有让我困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢雫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:52.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话…我还YY过各种下流的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事 你不用说出来也行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情可能和雫不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道了我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在想雫会不会离我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把刚刚说的那些话收回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:27.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等让春喜欢上我之后 我再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:50.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧 春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:01.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为春说想和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.49,setting3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz332.913\pos(626,370)}阿三哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.49,setting3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz332.427\pos(365,435)}优山要来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫 别回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 随便找个地方过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:30.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然如此轻松地推翻了我的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么…多么麻烦的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是吉田 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…雫 这位是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说今晚不想回家住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆也 晚饭吃了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:09.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不…陋室而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老妈不在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要住在客房吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 随便找个地方过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间 忍不住想象了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炒饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:35.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雫做的吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚不是看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有腌菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厉害啊 简直就像乡下的老婆婆似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不是说过别来这儿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:12.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优山！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:32.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你家里有座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:36.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在别人家里 你这是什么打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 在家里还学习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛不知道看向哪里才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真闲啊 玩文字接龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:51.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:56.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…但是爸爸也总是只穿一条内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是就这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:02.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微看一眼的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡的话就到被窝里睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:21.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我还带了特产过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:25.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 满善给我倒杯茶来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:40.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春真是个胆小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你能躲我到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得样子有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 为什么你们会在颜料喷雾贩售处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:35.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:37.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是因为要涂鸦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往公共物品上涂鸦的行为是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:43.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己家的东西上涂鸦有什么不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他家院子里全是雕刻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:49.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说为什么不良少年都爱往墙上涂鸦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:51.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那里有面墙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:52.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是小孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:54.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:56.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院子？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是雕刻？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.18,0:24:02.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢艺术的有钱人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:04.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人吃惊…
